article:
This is a 'list of current heads of state and government', showing heads of
State and heads of Government where different, mainly in parliamentary systems;
often a leader is both in presidential systems. Some states have semi-
presidential systems where the head of government role is fulfilled by both the
listed head of government and the head of state.

The list includes the names of the recently elected or appointed heads of state
who will take office on an appointed date.
categories: Lists of current office-holders|State Heads of state current
headings: States recognised by the United Nations
